title: The Quest for Greatness The Lake Travis High School Story by JPT
description:
Documentary about a High school football team The Lake Travis Cavaliers that won an unprecedented five consecutive state championships in football.
 No other football program has ever won 5 straight 4A state titles.

 This documentary will go back to when Lake Travis opened it's doors in the early 80's and take you on journey to when the Cavs made the playoffs for the first time in 2000 to the hiring of Jeff Dicus and the school's first state title in football. Despite changes at head coach when Chad Morris replaced Dicus, to when Hank Carter replaced Morris, the Cavs have kept on winning state titles. Take a ride with us as we take you behind the scenes of how it all happened.
